## 5. Query Examples
Example 1
Get all students with attendance below 75%.
SOQL
SELECT Name, Attendance__c
FROM Student__c
WHERE Attendance__c < 75
  
Example 2
Get all students whose fee status is pending.
SOQL
SELECT Name, Fee_Status__c
FROM Student__c
WHERE Fee_Status__c = 'Pending'
  
Example 3
Get all students enrolled in Computer Science course.
SOQL
SELECT Name, Course__c
FROM Student__c
WHERE Course__c = 'Computer Science'
  
Example 4
Get students eligible for placements.
SOQL
SELECT Name, CGPA__c
FROM Student__c
WHERE CGPA__c >= 7
  
Example 5
Get all faculty members handling more than 3 courses.
SOQL
SELECT Name
FROM Faculty__c
WHERE Number_of_Courses__c > 3

  
## 6. Reflection

Enterprise systems manage large amounts of continuously changing data. Manual monitoring is difficult and inefficient.

Triggers and automation help systems react immediately when data changes occur. This allows organizations to:

Maintain accurate data
Reduce manual work
Improve efficiency
Enforce business rules
Provide faster services
